<blockquote>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">SCP-4428:</span> <span style="font-family: 'Courier', monospace; font-weight: bold; margin: 2px 1px 1px 1px; background-color: #a3cef1;">Dr. Michaels is not in danger.</span><br />
<strong>Authors:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5190300); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5190300&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576548576" alt="Henzoid" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5190300)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5190300); return false;">Henzoid</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576548576" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735419); return false;">Lt Flops</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<p>This was a collab between <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5190300); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5190300&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576548576" alt="Henzoid" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5190300)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/henzoid" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5190300); return false;">Henzoid</a></span> and I. It's the first time I've written for the DoMc and I can't put into words how thrilling it was.</p>
<p>There will be no spoilers. Hope you enjoy, and happy Spooktober 👻!</p>
