<p>What better way to celebrate SpookyMonth than with an article about <strong>A COMPLETELY NORMAL RESEARCHER JUST LIVING HIS LIFE</strong></p>
<p>What a fun ride, collaborating with Floppy was great, and the DoMC is always so exciting to write with.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
